						               													<description>Welcome to Kajunga, An adventuress game which combines fast decision making, clever resource management and bold risk taking! In this game you are the survivors on a lost island, racing down on a path full of surprises on your way to the rescue boat and Black-Beards legendary treasure.&amp;#10;Mystery, adventure and team play in a rich tropical atmosphere for the young and young at heart.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How To Play?&amp;#10;The aim of the game is to be the &amp;#239;&amp;#172;&amp;#129;rst to reach the treasure / boat at the end of  the track. Each player picks a character to play with and rolls the dice. He then moves according to the number on the dice. The player can change the number of moves by using his money coins. The player must perform the action dictated by the square he landed on.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;After the &amp;#239;&amp;#172;&amp;#129;rst two rounds of the game the black pirate joins in. He is the one who owns the treasure. During the game he chases all the players, sending them back on their tracks and laying traps. The player can try to defend himself against the pirates by using the objects he can collect on the track.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game includes many surprises and unpredictable twists. Most of the moves are determined by the players who hold in their hand diamonds, gold coins, gold keys. Also traps and deals with other opponents can easily change the course of  the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
